 systems may not very common, they are more\nlikely to happen in systems with close-in, massive planets, with F- and G-type\nhost-stars and stellar metallicities $\\mathrm{[Fe/H]} > 0.2$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 Jul 2022 17:25:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 11 Nov 2022 17:29:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-14"}
