 advantage, BDPC involves minor modifications to the\n6TiSCH protocol stack, which makes it compatible with current implementations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 Jul 2022 22:44:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 31 Aug 2022 12:39:35 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 29 Jan 2023 01:37:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-31"}
